WEBVTT

00:00:29.683 --> 00:00:31.179
našao sam ovu slatku malu pjesmu,

00:00:31.179 --> 00:00:32.780
"Četiri ujutro."

00:00:32.780 --> 00:00:34.045
"Sat od noći do dana.

00:00:34.045 --> 00:00:35.431
Sat od strane do strane.

00:00:35.431 --> 00:00:37.229
Sat za one koji su prošli tridesetu..."

00:00:37.229 --> 00:00:39.316
I ide dalje, ali čim sam pročitao ovu pjesmu,

00:00:39.316 --> 00:00:41.239
zaljubio sam se u nju,

00:00:41.239 --> 00:00:44.180
tako snažno, da sam posumnjao da smo se sreli

00:00:44.180 --> 00:00:45.593
negdje prije.

00:00:45.593 --> 00:00:47.892
Jesam li se vozio u liftu s ovom pjesmom?

00:00:47.892 --> 00:00:49.412
Jesam li očijukao s ovom pjesmom

00:00:49.412 --> 00:00:50.557
u nekom kafiću negdje?

00:00:50.557 --> 00:00:52.069
Nisam to mogao smjestiti, i mučilo me,

00:00:52.069 --> 00:00:53.971
i onda u sljedećih tjedan ili dva

00:00:53.971 --> 00:00:55.420
gledao bih stari film,

00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:56.702
i ovo bi se dogodilo.

00:00:56.702 --> 00:00:57.965
(Video) Groucho Marx: Charlie, trebao si doći na prvu zabavu.

00:00:57.965 --> 00:01:00.317
Nismo došli kući do četiri ujutro.